---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
    title="Privacy Policy - JSON Utility Kit"
    description="Read our clear privacy policies. We process all formatting, minifying, and conversion locally in your browser. Zero uploads, zero logs."
>
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 py-16 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="border-b border-gray-200 pb-8 dark:border-gray-800 mb-8">
            <h1
                class="text-3xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-gray-900 dark:text-white sm:text-4xl"
            >
                Privacy Policy
            </h1>
            <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">
                Last updated: June 12, 2026
            </p>
        </div>

        <div
            class="prose dark:prose-invert max-w-none text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 space-y-6 leading-relaxed"
        >
            <p>
                At <strong>JSON Utility Kit</strong>, we take your private code
                configuration and data confidentiality extremely seriously. We
                want you to fully understand what happens to your data when you
                use our web service.
            </p>

            <h2
                class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mt-8 mb-4"
            >
                1. Local Client-Side Data Processing
            </h2>
            <p>
                The core utilities provided on this website, including but not
                limited to the <strong
                    >JSON Formatter, JSON Validator, JSON Beautifier, JSON
                    Viewer, JSON Minifier, JSON Editor, JSON to CSV, and CSV to
                    JSON converters</strong
                >, process your entered data entirely client-side.
            </p>
            <p class="font-semibold text-brand-700 dark:text-brand-400">
                None of the data you enter, paste, import, or upload into our
                textboxes is transmitted to our servers or stored in any
                databases. All actions are handled inside the memory space of
                your own local web browser (Sandboxed Javascript engine).
            </p>

            <h2
                class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mt-8 mb-4"
            >
                2. Cookies and Logs
            </h2>
            <p>
                We may use cookies to remember your interface preferences (such
                as your chosen theme setting like Light/Dark mode). Standard
                server-side webserver logs may collect technical metadata like
                your IP address, browser user-agent, referrers, and visit times
                to monitor system performance and secure page routing stability.
            </p>

            <h2
                class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mt-8 mb-4"
            >
                3. Third-Party Analytics
            </h2>
            <p>
                We may employ lightweight privacy-conscious analytics services
                (like Google Analytics) to aggregate anonymous usage statistics,
                such as total monthly page visits and popular tools. No personal
                identifier data or text input pasted inside our tools is ever
                tracked or logged by these analytical modules.
            </p>

            <h2
                class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mt-8 mb-4"
            >
                4. Advertising Programs (Google AdSense)
            </h2>
            <p>
                This website may present advertisement segments supported by
                third-party ad engines such as Google AdSense. Google uses
                cookies (like the DART cookie) to serve relevant advertisements
                to users based on prior clicks and visits. You can elect to
                decline personalized ads in your web browser or by reviewing
                Google’s main privacy parameters.
            </p>

            <h2
                class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mt-8 mb-4"
            >
                5. Contact Information
            </h2>
            <p>
                If you have any questions regarding this Privacy Policy
                document, feel free to email us at <span
                    class="font-semibold text-brand-600 dark:text-brand-400 font-mono"
                    >privacy@jsonutilitykit.com</span
                >.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</Layout>
